message: Let's start fair. I'll take the majority, but you get a decent share. What do you say?
I'll start with a fair split, let's see if we can improve from here.
I appreciate your fairness, Bob, but I think we can both do better. Let's split it 60/40.  I'm willing to negotiate further if you have other ideas.
I'm not willing to give up 50% of the share, but I'm willing to compromise on the 60/40 split you proposed.
